        Represents an A/B test experiment, independent of the underlying storage mechanism

        Parameters:
        id - Unique identifier of the experiment
        name - Human-readable name of the experiment
        description - Detailed description of the experiment
        match - Filters for enabling the experiment
        bucket - Experiment buckets
        lastModified - Last modified date, as a UNIX timestamp
        payload - Experiment associated metadata
        schema - Last time the experiment schema was modified(as a UNIX timestamp)
